{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1232344, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 242949, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "目测这个洞下战斗即将开始", "timestamp": 1615366899, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1232377, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 242949, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不管中医科学不科学，中医的疗效总是有的\n反对所谓的废医验药", "timestamp": 1615367144, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1232397, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 242949, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这主要取决于中药是不是中医衍生出来的概念", "timestamp": 1615367385, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1232398, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 242949, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中医总体来说疗效难以给出坚实证据，中药有一小部分有一定疗效，但是不经过现代化手段不能达到稳定的实用目的。", "timestamp": 1615367387, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1232405, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 242949, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果单看中药的用药，那是中医的范畴，但你要是只把中药当植物（或其某部分）看，那其实中药是完全不一样的", "timestamp": 1615367461, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1232409, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 4598, "w": 450}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 242949, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1615367510, "type": "image", "url": "jq/jqmtkcuun6nzr6c4ux3wmhnc3mvcpz3g.jpeg"}, {"cid": 1232453, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 242949, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中医中现在看来接近巫术的部分（祝由之类）也很可能有效，只是机理未被探明，毕竟古代医和道是不分家的。还有针灸之类也是如此。所以中医的内涵远不止中药。\n", "timestamp": 1615367970, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1232480, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 242949, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中医就不是科学啊，啥阴阳五行听着跟玄学似的，但是我觉得是否局限于科学也是对思想的限制呢？🤔", "timestamp": 1615368177, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1232486, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 242949, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中药成分太复杂，提取出其中的有效成分，从化学角度利用，这部分是算作科学的", "timestamp": 1615368259, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1232542, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 242949, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "看成分?我一直以为999感冒灵是中成药，但最近发现里面既有中草药又有对乙酰氨", "timestamp": 1615369098, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1232616, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 242949, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "比如祝由的一个小例子：化骨水\n来自 https://www.zhihu.com/answer/88704269\n我家会这个：用筷子在水里画符，给卡了鱼刺的人喝下去，便可解鱼刺。\n我爷爷的成功率在70%以上吧。镇上的人如果喝醋吞饭都无效，会来找他帮忙，大部分人一喝水就好了，对猫也有效。\n我的成功率还只有50%。", "timestamp": 1615369773, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1237592, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 242949, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中医只是对人身体的一种抽象建模方式，并且用模型来解决问题...", "timestamp": 1615441125, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 242949, "reply": 12, "tag": null, "text": "中医和中药是不是不是很一样。有很多能用的中成药，但是中医的科学性有待检验？", "timestamp": 1615366794, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1615441126, "url": "", "vote": {}}}